detail.name: Khai
detail.effect: [On Play] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck, then reveal up to 1 card with a cost of 4 or less and 《Pride Troopers》 in its special traits and add it to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of its owner's deck in a random order.

detail.name: カイ
detail.effect: 【登場時】自分のデッキの上から5枚を見て、コスト4以下の特徴《プライド・トルーパーズ》を持つカード1枚までを公開し、手札に加える。残りをランダムにデッキの下に置く。
